Description: Tools to extract information from the Intergovernmental 
    Organizations Database ('IGO'), version 3, provided by the Correlates of 
    War Project <https://correlatesofwar.org/>.
    Pevehouse, Jon C.W., Timothy Nordstron, Roseanne W McManus, 
    Anne Spencer Jamison, “Tracking Organizations in the World: The Correlates 
    of War 'IGO' Version 3.0 datasets”, Journal of Peace Research
    <doi:10.1177/0022343319881175>. Version 3 includes information from 1815 to
    2014.
